{"tid":829594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"指插男高中生8分鐘　男師被逮稱「滿足性慾」","createTime":"2018-09-20T14:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T16:02:58.000Z","uid":1426,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7b6821d549ad596c2100ab8808bfe1c2a00661","tid":829594,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180915/640_d623476ffbd9b93f907a0061838d203b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180915%2F640_d623476ffbd9b93f907a0061838d203b.jpg&h=eb664898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指插男高中生8分鐘　男師被逮稱「滿足性慾」。翻攝自TBS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本一名國小男老師，用手指伸進男高中生的口中，並且還按壓喉結，涉嫌施暴遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據《TBS》報導，遭到逮捕的千葉市公立小學29歲老師中村將，涉嫌在8月11日，於千葉大學正門前，攔住一名17歲男高中生搭話，稱「牙齒排列很漂亮，按壓這邊的話會嗝氣喔」，並把他帶到大學內的廁所，然後用手指伸入口中，並且按壓喉結、牙齦，時間長達8分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n對於警方的調查，中村將坦承犯行，稱是「為了滿足性的欲求」，喜歡嗝氣的味道，還說「從幾年前就在千葉市內做同樣的事情，有幾十次了」。對於老師發生這種事情，千葉市的教育長表示「感到相當的遺憾，可能會導致民眾對教育行政、學校教育的不信任，在此致上最大的歉意」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180915/640_0560d440ad649f9b7f16b828fa8128a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180915%2F640_0560d440ad649f9b7f16b828fa8128a9.jpg&h=f7387391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180915/640_50378184330a99776b634805949d198a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180915%2F640_50378184330a99776b634805949d198a.jpg&h=c445b835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/mGv0ZD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FmGv0ZD.gif&h=192ef3fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2732383c2569ae255617d69b30ae1229efa72720","tid":829594,"uid":1426,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https